{"tid":527764,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"法律專家召喚","createTime":"2018-01-13T04:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T10:21:05.000Z","uid":51746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b11caa849f4c940cd5ea05b1d98fd05c3ed0ddb5","tid":527764,"uid":51746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T04:41:16.000Z","msg":"最近有親人過左身無留遺囑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於無遺囑同埋有個幾歲大嘅細佬,<br />\n機緣巧合下我同另一位親人成為左遺產管理人。<br />\n<br />\n但係個位親人咩文件都唔簽淨係攪啲佢可以直接收錢嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家9成野做唔到<br />\n想問下我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2e28d0d80b4e750cb5a2805cd0295534bc0408","tid":527764,"uid":61832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"俾番哂啲錢個小朋友啦你倆個仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c2847bd22e0963f587448e83e4d04bea690645","tid":527764,"uid":51746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:04:12.000Z","msg":"個細路係我細佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n父母都走左好耐  而家叔叔走埋但個女人淨係簽佢收錢嘅文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de5aa1a68ca2244023d6056eafa49d222462006","tid":527764,"uid":51746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T09:24:13.000Z","msg":"有無人幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7795911cdfe5188bbb04e3cf0d30aea659e364a","tid":527764,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5de5aa1a68ca2244023d6056eafa49d222462006","tid":527764,"uid":51746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T09:24:13.000Z","msg":"有無人幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"好 我幫下手 wait"},{"pid":"fd1fa86d39ae805e69aa11b718bc93ec7e296c65","tid":527764,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T09:39:20.000Z","msg":"其實點解唔正正經經搵個律師處理？"},{"pid":"ae13bebf0f4b21524907284185e358babb2c4b2d","tid":527764,"uid":51746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解唔正正經經搵個律師處理？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一路都有律師幫手申報野<br />\n但佢唔可以強迫人簽名<br />\n<br />\n因為叔叔無其他親人所以遺產左比我地<br />\n但由於我細佬未成年所以要搵多個人做管理人<br />\n<br />\n但屌佢老味間個女人中先上去見下律師有著數先簽名<br />\n咩撚野都唔簽攪到公司停哂運作咁濟"}]}